{\pos(289.275)}Bye!

1898
00:46:19.735 --> 00:46:21.653
{\pos(289.275)}(DEVICE POWERING DOWN)

1899
00:46:27.493 --> 00:46:28.493
{\pos(289.275)}(GASPS)

1900
00:46:40.715 --> 00:46:41.715
{\pos(289.275)}(EXHALES)

1901
00:46:43.676 --> 00:46:44.634
{\pos(289.275)}(CRACKING)

1902
00:46:44.719 --> 00:46:46.344
{\pos(289.275)}(SHUDDERING)

1903
00:47:02.695 --> 00:47:05.321
{\pos(289.275)}(THEME MUSIC PLAYING ON TV)

1904
00:47:09.285 --> 00:47:11.745
{\pos(289.275)}(MAN CHATTERING ON TV)

1905
00:47:11.829 --> 00:47:13.204
{\pos(289.275)}(SOFTLY)
Come on!

1906
00:47:27.136 --> 00:47:28.428
{\pos(289.275)}(GROANS)

1907
00:47:35.269 --> 00:47:37.103
{\pos(289.275)}(GRUNTS) What the...

1908
00:47:39.940 --> 00:47:41.608
{\pos(289.275)}Quiet down. fish!

1909
00:47:48.616 --> 00:47:49.657
{\pos(289.275)}Down. boy!

1910
00:48:11.305 --> 00:48:12.722
{\pos(289.275)}Ah-ha! (LAUGHING)

1911
00:48:12.807 --> 00:48:16.142
{\pos(289.275)}We did it!
Come on. girls. let's go!

1912
00:48:24.026 --> 00:48:27.111
{\pos(289.275)}But what about
the other people
who ordered cookies?

1913
00:48:27.196 --> 00:48:29.906
{\pos(289.275)}Life is full of
disappointments

1914
00:48:29.990 --> 00:48:32.742
{\pos(289.275)}for some people.
(CHUCKLING)

1915
00:48:33.661 --> 00:48:35.161
{\pos(289.275)}(SCREAMING)
(EXCLAIMS)

1916
00:48:36.080 --> 00:48:37.413
{\pos(289.275)}(SCREAMING)

1917
00:48:37.498 --> 00:48:38.998
{\pos(289.275)}Don't do that!

1918
00:48:39.083 --> 00:48:42.126
{\pos(289.275)}Super Silly Fun Land!
Can we go? Please?

1919
00:48:42.545 --> 00:48:43.586
{\pos(289.275)}No.

1920
00:48:43.671 --> 00:48:46.172
{\pos(289.275)}But we've never been.
And it's the funnest
place on earth!

1921
00:48:46.257 --> 00:48:47.298
{\pos(289.275)}Don't care.

1922
00:48:47.383 --> 00:48:48.508
{\pos(289.275)}Please?
Please?

1923
00:48:48.592 --> 00:48:50.260
{\pos(289.275)}We'll never ask
for anything else.
ever again!

1924
00:48:50.344 --> 00:48:52.387
{\pos(289.275)}Pretty please?
Please?

1925
00:48:59.520 --> 00:49:01.479
{\pos(289.275)}Come on!
Come on!

1926
00:49:02.022 --> 00:49:04.190
{\pos(289.275)}Light bulb.

1927
00:49:09.113 --> 00:49:10.905
{\pos(289.275)}Come on!

1928
00:49:10.990 --> 00:49:13.950
{\pos(289.275)}Goodbye. have fun.

1929
00:49:17.371 --> 00:49:20.915
{\pos(289.275)}Sorry. dude.
They can't ride
without an adult.

1930
00:49:21.000 --> 00:49:22.375
{\pos(289.275)}What?

1931
00:49:22.459 --> 00:49:24.335
{\pos(289.275)}(SIGHS IN FRUSTRATION)

1932
00:49:29.550 --> 00:49:32.010
{\pos(289.275)}(GIRLS WHOOPING)

1933
00:49:36.348 --> 00:49:37.891
{\pos(289.275)}(ALL SCREAMING)

1934
00:50:11.300 --> 00:50:12.967
{\pos(289.275)}(RETCHING)

1935
00:50:18.891 --> 00:50:20.308
{\pos(289.275)}AGNES: (SQUEALS)
Oh. my gosh!

1936
00:50:20.392 --> 00:50:22.810
{\pos(289.275)}Look at that
fluffy unicorn!

1937
00:50:25.564 --> 00:50:27.857
{\pos(289.275)}He's so fluffy.
I'm gonna die!

1938
00:50:27.942 --> 00:50:29.359
{\pos(289.275)}You've gotta let
us play for it!

1939
00:50:29.443 --> 00:50:31.194
{\pos(289.275)}No. no. no.

1940
00:50:31.278 --> 00:50:32.570
{\pos(289.275)}Come on!

1941
00:50:34.114 --> 00:50:36.658
{\pos(289.275)}How much for
the fluffy unicorn?

1942
00:50:36.742 --> 00:50:37.784
{\pos(289.275)}(LAUGHING)

1943
00:50:37.868 --> 00:50:39.744
{\pos(289.275)}Well. it is not
for sale.

1944
00:50:39.828 --> 00:50:41.746
{\pos(289.275)}But all you gotta do
to win it

1945
00:50:41.830 --> 00:50:44.832
{\pos(289.275)}is knock down that
little spaceship there.

1946
00:50:45.709 --> 00:50:46.834
{\pos(289.275)}It's easy!

1947
00:50:55.219 --> 00:50:56.469
{\pos(289.275)}Yay!

1948
00:51:08.482 --> 00:51:09.649
{\pos(289.275)}Again!

1949
00:51:10.401 --> 00:51:12.819
{\pos(289.275)}Wait!
Come on.
One more time!

1950
00:51:12.903 --> 00:51:14.070
{\pos(289.275)}Just one more.

1951
00:51:14.154 --> 00:51:16.531
{\pos(289.275)}I accidentally
closed my eyes.

1952
00:51:31.880 --> 00:51:33.881
{\pos(289.275)}I hit it!
I hit it!
That was cool.

1953
00:51:35.551 --> 00:51:36.759
{\pos(289.275)}Aw!

1954
00:51:38.345 --> 00:51:41.222
{\pos(289.275)}Whoa. whoa. whoa.
What was that?

1955
00:51:41.974 --> 00:51:45.059
{\pos(289.275)}She hit that.
I saw that with
my own eyes.

1956
00:51:45.144 --> 00:51:47.895
{\pos(289.275)}Hey. buddy.
let me explain
something to you.

1957
00:51:47.980 --> 00:51:50.231
{\pos(289.275)}You see that
little tin spaceship?

1958
00:51:50.315 --> 00:51:52.483
{\pos(289.275)}You see how
it's not knocked over?

1959
00:51:52.568 --> 00:51:55.445
{\pos(289.275)}Do you know what
that means. professor?

1960
00:51:55.529 --> 00:51:59.032
{\pos(289.275)}It means you don't
get the unicorn!

1961
00:51:59.116 --> 00:52:01.117
{\pos(289.275)}Oh! Uh-oh!

1962
00:52:01.201 --> 00:52:03.036
{\pos(289.275)}Somebody's got
a frowny face.

1963
00:52:03.120 --> 00:52:05.538
{\pos(289.275)}Boo! Better luck
next time!

1964
00:52:07.791 --> 00:52:10.501
{\pos(289.275)}Okay. my turn.

1965
00:52:31.899 --> 00:52:34.442
{\pos(289.275)}Knocked over!

1966
00:52:38.781 --> 00:52:40.573
{\pos(289.275)}It's so fluffy!

1967
00:52:40.657 --> 00:52:41.657
{\pos(289.275)}Yeah!

1968
00:52:42.326 --> 00:52:44.410
{\pos(289.275)}That was awesome!

1969
00:52:44.495 --> 00:52:46.162
{\pos(289.275)}You blew up
the whole thing!

1970
00:52:46.246 --> 00:52:48.623
{\pos(289.275)}Let's go.
Let's try
another game!

1971
00:52:53.086 --> 00:52:54.587
{\pos(289.275)}(ALL LAUGHING)

1972
00:52:55.672 --> 00:52:58.090
{\pos(289.275)}Gru. do you mind
if I have a quick word?

1973
00:52:58.842 --> 00:53:01.093
{\pos(289.275)}Okay. girls. go play.

1974
00:53:08.644 --> 00:53:10.937
{\pos(289.275)}I got the shrink ray!

1975
00:53:13.565 --> 00:53:15.775
{\pos(289.275)}Cotton candy!

1976
00:53:16.777 --> 00:53:20.696
{\pos(289.275)}We have 12 days
until the moon is
in optimum position.

1977
00:53:20.781 --> 00:53:22.949
{\pos(289.275)}We can't afford
any distractions!

1978
00:53:24.701 --> 00:53:25.952
{\pos(289.275)}Get me Perkins.

1979
00:53:32.125 --> 00:53:33.292
{\pos(289.275)}Ah-ha!

1980
00:53:33.961 --> 00:53:36.087
{\pos(289.275)}Sorry to bother you.
Mr. Perkins.

1981
00:53:36.171 --> 00:53:40.174
{\pos(289.275)}but I figured that you
would want to see this!

1982
00:53:40.968 --> 00:53:42.093
{\pos(289.275)}What?

1983
00:53:54.606 --> 00:53:55.982
{\pos(289.275)}Well done. Gru.
(SQUEAKING)

1984
00:53:56.066 --> 00:53:57.066
{\pos(289.275)}Rather impressive.

1985
00:53:57.150 --> 00:54:00.152
{\pos(289.275)}Now. the rest
of the plan is simple.

1986
00:54:00.821 --> 00:54:04.574
{\pos(289.275)}I fly to the moon.
I shrink the moon.

1987
00:54:04.658 --> 00:54:08.369
{\pos(289.275)}I grab the moon.
I sit on the toilet.

1988
00:54:08.453 --> 00:54:10.079
{\pos(289.275)}What?
(GIRLS LAUGHING)

1989
00:54:10.163 --> 00:54:12.248
{\pos(289.275)}Sorry. Sorry!

1990
00:54:12.332 --> 00:54:15.459
{\pos(289.275)}Could you excuse me
for just one second?

1991
00:54:15.544 --> 00:54:16.961
{\pos(289.275)}I told you not
to touch my things.

1992
00:54:17.045 --> 00:54:20.089
{\pos(289.275)}I told you. I told you.
I've told you
a thousand times.

1993
00:54:20.173 --> 00:54:21.841
{\pos(289.275)}Hey. can we
order pizza?

1994
00:54:21.925 --> 00:54:23.843
{\pos(289.275)}Pizza?
You just had lunch.

1995
00:54:23.927 --> 00:54:25.094
{\pos(289.275)}Not now. for dinner.

1996
00:54:25.178 --> 00:54:26.762
{\pos(289.275)}Dinner?

1997
00:54:26.847 --> 00:54:29.640
{\pos(289.275)}Just...
Fine. fine. fine. whatever.
Just get back in there!

1998
00:54:29.725 --> 00:54:31.559
{\pos(289.275)}Oh! Can we get
stuffed crust?

1999
00:54:31.685 --> 00:54:32.727
{\pos(289.275)}(EXCLAIMING)

2000
00:54:32.811 --> 00:54:34.020
{\pos(289.275)}Stuffed crust!
Stuffed crust!

2001
00:54:34.104 --> 00:54:35.688
{\pos(289.275)}I'll stuff you
all in the crust!

2002
00:54:35.772 --> 00:54:37.106
{\pos(289.275)}(GIGGLING)

2003
00:54:37.691 --> 00:54:39.108
{\pos(289.275)}You're funny!

2004
00:54:39.192 --> 00:54:41.944
{\pos(289.275)}Just don't come out
of that room again!

2005
00:54:42.487 --> 00:54:43.529
{\pos(289.275)}All right.

2006
00:54:44.448 --> 00:54:47.825
{\pos(289.275)}Sorry about that.
Where were we?

2007
00:54:47.910 --> 00:54:49.493
{\pos(289.275)}You were sitting
on the toilet.

2008
00:54:49.578 --> 00:54:54.123
{\pos(289.275)}No. no. no!
No. I'm sorry. It was
a little attempt at humor.

2009
00:54:54.207 --> 00:54:57.043
{\pos(289.275)}I know how much
you like to laugh

2010
00:54:59.504 --> 00:55:03.341
{\pos(289.275)}inside.
Now. I was saying...

2011
00:55:03.467 --> 00:55:05.217
{\pos(289.275)}(DOOR CREAKING OPEN)

2012
00:55:06.929 --> 00:55:08.846
{\pos(289.275)}You don't seem
terribly focused. Gru.

2013
00:55:08.931 --> 00:55:11.265
{\pos(289.275)}Believe me.
I am completely focused.

2014
00:55:11.391 --> 00:55:13.434
{\pos(289.275)}Hello! Whoa!
What?

2015
00:55:13.518 --> 00:55:14.644
{\pos(289.275)}That guy is huge!

2016
00:55:14.728 --> 00:55:16.145
{\pos(289.275)}Are we on TV?
What are those? Children?

2017
00:55:16.229 --> 00:55:19.065
{\pos(289.275)}What are you doing?
I told you to stay
out of here!

2018
00:55:19.149 --> 00:55:20.733
{\pos(289.275)}(GIRLS LAUGHING)

2019
00:55:24.279 --> 00:55:25.488
{\pos(289.275)}No. no. no!

2020
00:55:25.572 --> 00:55:26.656
{\pos(289.275)}Freeze ray!

2021
00:55:26.740 --> 00:55:28.324
{\pos(289.275)}Mr. Gru?

2022
00:55:28.408 --> 00:55:30.368
{\pos(289.275)}(GRU EXCLAIMING)

2023
00:55:33.080 --> 00:55:34.413
{\pos(289.275)}Okay.

2024
00:55:35.791 --> 00:55:37.166
{\pos(289.275)}As I was saying...

2025
00:55:37.250 --> 00:55:41.087
{\pos(289.275)}No need to continue.
I've seen quite enough.

2026
00:55:41.171 --> 00:55:42.338
{\pos(289.275)}But my plan...

2027
00:55:42.422 --> 00:55:43.506
{\pos(289.275)}Is a great plan.

2028
00:55:43.590 --> 00:55:46.801
{\pos(289.275)}I love everything
about your plan.
except for one thing.

2029
00:55:47.678 --> 00:55:49.011
{\pos(289.275)}You.

2030
00:55:52.265 --> 00:55:55.851
{\pos(289.275)}Look. Mom.
I drew a picture of me
landing on the moon!

2031
00:55:56.895 --> 00:55:58.854
{\pos(289.275)}(EXCLAIMS INDIFFERENTLY)

2032
00:55:58.939 --> 00:56:02.984
{\pos(289.275)}Look. Mom. I made
a prototype of the rocket
out of macaroni!

2033
00:56:03.944 --> 00:56:05.236
{\pos(289.275)}(EXCLAIMS INDIFFERENTLY)

2034
00:56:05.612 --> 00:56:07.571
{\pos(289.275)}Look. Mom.
I made a real rocket

2035
00:56:07.656 --> 00:56:09.991
{\pos(289.275)}based on the
macaroni prototype!

2036
00:56:12.285 --> 00:56:13.494
{\pos(289.275)}(GASPS)

2037
00:56:14.204 --> 00:56:16.163
{\pos(289.275)}(EXCLAIMS INDIFFERENTLY)

2038
00:56:21.253 --> 00:56:23.004
{\pos(289.275)}I don't understand.

2039
00:56:23.338 --> 00:56:25.631
{\pos(289.275)}Let's face reality. Gru.

2040
00:56:25.716 --> 00:56:30.469
{\pos(289.275)}You've been at this
for far too long with
far too little success.

2041
00:56:30.679 --> 00:56:34.890
{\pos(289.275)}We're gonna put our faith.
our money. into a...

2042
00:56:35.726 --> 00:56:37.351
{\pos(289.275)}Well. a younger villain.

2043
00:56:37.436 --> 00:56:38.894
{\pos(289.275)}But I...

2044
00:56:38.979 --> 00:56:41.105
{\pos(289.275)}It's over. Goodbye. Gru.

2045
00:56:53.618 --> 00:56:55.494
{\pos(289.275)}(INDISTINCT MUTTERING)

2046
00:56:56.830 --> 00:56:58.039
{\pos(289.275)}(SIGHS)

2047
00:57:02.335 --> 00:57:06.839
{\pos(289.275)}Now. I know there have been
some rumors going around

2048
00:57:06.923 --> 00:57:10.217
{\pos(289.275)}that the bank is
no longer funding us.

2049
00:57:11.094 --> 00:57:13.888
{\pos(289.275)}Well. I am here to put
those rumors to rest.

2050
00:57:16.016 --> 00:57:17.933
{\pos(289.275)}They are true.

2051
00:57:18.018 --> 00:57:19.810
{\pos(289.275)}(ALL GASP)
Uh-oh!

2052
00:57:19.895 --> 00:57:22.104
{\pos(289.275)}In terms of money.

2053
00:57:23.273 --> 00:57:25.441
{\pos(289.275)}we have no money.

2054
00:57:25.525 --> 00:57:28.110
{\pos(289.275)}So how will we
get to the moon?

2055
00:57:29.279 --> 00:57:31.113
{\pos(289.275)}The answer is clear.

2056
00:57:31.198 --> 00:57:32.782
{\pos(289.275)}We won't.

2057
00:57:33.700 --> 00:57:34.992
{\pos(289.275)}(SOBBING)

2058
00:57:35.827 --> 00:57:38.120
{\pos(289.275)}We are doomed.

2059
00:57:39.372 --> 00:57:41.957
{\pos(289.275)}Now would probably
be a good time

2060
00:57:42.042 --> 00:57:43.959
{\pos(289.275)}to look for other
employment options.

2061
00:57:44.044 --> 00:57:45.377
{\pos(289.275)}(ALL GASP)

2062
00:57:45.879 --> 00:57:46.962
{\pos(289.275)}I know.

2063
00:57:47.047 --> 00:57:52.301
{\pos(289.275)}I have fired up my resume
as I suggest that
all of you do. as well.

2064
00:57:53.303 --> 00:57:54.887
{\pos(289.275)}What is it?

2065
00:57:56.807 --> 00:58:00.101
{\pos(289.275)}Can't you see that
I am in the middle
of a pep talk?

2066
00:58:18.245 --> 00:58:19.995
{\pos(289.275)}(MINION EXCLAIMING)

2067
00:58:20.413 --> 00:58:21.747
{\pos(289.275)}(LAUGHING)

2068
00:58:21.915 --> 00:58:25.709
{\pos(289.275)}(ALL EXCLAIMING)

2069
00:58:29.756 --> 00:58:31.132
{\pos(289.275)}Yes!

2070
00:58:31.216 --> 00:58:34.135
{\pos(289.275)}Yes. we will build
our own rocket

2071
00:58:34.761 --> 00:58:38.305
{\pos(289.275)}using this and whatever
else we can find!

2072
00:58:38.765 --> 00:58:42.393
{\pos(289.275)}Grab everything!
Hit the junkyards!
Take apart the cars!

2073
00:58:42.894 --> 00:58:44.770
{\pos(289.275)}Who needs the bank?

2074
00:58:44.855 --> 00:58:46.605
{\pos(289.275)}Let's go. Let's go!

2075
00:58:54.614 --> 00:58:56.615
{\pos(289.275)}(UPBEAT POP SONG PLAYING)

2076
00:59:01.997 --> 00:59:03.247
{\pos(289.275)}(SCREAMING)

2077
00:59:12.757 --> 00:59:14.133
{\pos(289.275)}(BLEEPING)

2078
00:59:36.573 --> 00:59:38.866
{\pos(289.275)}(GASPS) Mom!
What are you doing here?

2079
00:59:38.950 --> 00:59:41.785
{\pos(289.275)}And here he is
in the bathtub.

2080
00:59:41.953 --> 00:59:44.163
{\pos(289.275)}Oh! Look at his
little buns.

2081
00:59:44.581 --> 00:59:46.165
{\pos(289.275)}(GIRLS GIGGLING)

2082
00:59:46.499 --> 00:59:47.958
{\pos(289.275)}Mom.

2083
00:59:48.043 --> 00:59:49.460
{\pos(289.275)}Not cool.

2084
00:59:50.462 --> 00:59:55.007
{\pos(289.275)}And here.
he's all dressed up
in his Sunday best.

2085
00:59:55.675 --> 00:59:57.301
{\pos(289.275)}He looks like a girl!

2086
00:59:57.385 --> 01:00:01.138
{\pos(289.275)}(CHUCKLES)
Yes. he does.
An ugly girl!

2087
01:00:05.977 --> 01:00:07.353
{\pos(289.275)}(WHOOPING)

2088
01:00:19.157 --> 01:00:20.199
{\pos(289.275)}(SNARLING)

2089
01:00:23.954 --> 01:00:25.537
{\pos(289.275)}You're funny!

2090
01:00:39.052 --> 01:00:42.012
{\pos(289.275)}Yes! Mine's shaped
like a dead guy!

2091
01:00:47.560 --> 01:00:48.936
{\pos(289.275)}(BLEEPING)

2092
01:00:51.564 --> 01:00:52.564
{\pos(289.275)}(BEEPING RAPIDLY)

2093
01:00:52.899 --> 01:00:54.566
{\pos(289.275)}(GIRLS GIGGLING)

2094
01:01:00.115 --> 01:01:02.658
{\pos(289.275)}RECEPTIONIST:
Mr. Perkins.
your son is here.

2095
01:01:02.742 --> 01:01:04.576
{\pos(289.275)}Send him in.

2096
01:01:05.745 --> 01:01:07.413
{\pos(289.275)}Hey. Dad.

2097
01:01:08.248 --> 01:01:09.665
{\pos(289.275)}You wanted to see me?

2098
01:01:09.749 --> 01:01:11.166
{\pos(289.275)}Yes. I did. Victor.

2099
01:01:11.251 --> 01:01:12.751
{\pos(289.275)}I am not Victor anymore.

2100
01:01:12.836 --> 01:01:16.297
{\pos(289.275)}Victor was my nerd name.
Now I am Vector!

2101
01:01:16.381 --> 01:01:17.715
{\pos(289.275)}Sit down!

2102
01:01:19.342 --> 01:01:21.760
{\pos(289.275)}Do you know where
the shrink ray is?

2103
01:01:22.178 --> 01:01:24.138
{\pos(289.275)}Duh! Back at my place.

2104
01:01:24.222 --> 01:01:27.057
{\pos(289.275)}Oh. is that right?
Back at your place?
Oh. that's cool.

2105
01:01:27.142 --> 01:01:31.437
{\pos(289.275)}I guess Gru
must just have one
that looks exactly like it!

